{"tid":666141,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"以 project 企劃 形式 去 影相","createTime":"2018-05-15T15:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T10:50:22.000Z","uid":185452,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4519c29706167352fa4d7b2cf5c17c6077815a10","tid":666141,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T15:10:25.000Z","msg":"以下嘅 新聞 對我頗有 啟發。  365 攝影計劃 可能大家都聽得多，但 圍繞一個 特定 &ldquo;主體 &rdquo;去影，應該比較少。 <br />\n<br />\n我諗 要學習佢 嘅話，可以將難度降低，例如話 連續 影 2-3 個星期，針對 香港嘅電車，或者 尖沙咀 鐘樓 之類，運用不同嘅構圖 和 技巧去記錄。<br />\n<br />\n***************<br />\n<br />\n這一輯來自巴西攝影師 Tunisio Alves Filho 的作品，是大家耳熟能詳的 365 攝影計劃，但他的主題很清晰明確，就是圍繞一個著名景點 Barra Lighthouse，一座漂亮的燈塔。用一整年的時間，每天拍攝同一座建築物？有可能嗎？這就是「One Lighthouse, 365 Clicks」的有趣之處，一幅幅的作品，以不同的角度、技巧、道具來拍攝，畫面美麗之餘，也甚有創意！<br />\n<br />\n詳細新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://petapixel.com/2013/04/29/creative-365-project-captures-the-same-lighthouse-365-different-ways/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2F2013%2F04%2F29%2Fcreative-365-project-captures-the-same-lighthouse-365-different-ways%2F&d=l%2BKlAbT4fi%2BxrQMUUF1vPP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=42b9b4ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://petapixel.com/2013/04/29/creative-365-project-captures-the-same-lighthouse-365-different-ways/</a><br />\n<br />\n官方網頁，睇曬 365張相片<br />\n<a href=\"http://alvesfilho.com/365/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Falvesfilho.com%2F365%2F&d=l%2BKlAbT4fi%2BxrQMUUF1vPP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=38da8549\" target=\"_blank\">http://alvesfilho.com/365/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2013/04/Alves_filho-barra-lighthouse-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2FAlves_filho-barra-lighthouse-10.jpg&h=badd778e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2013/04/Alves_filho-barra-lighthouse-9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2FAlves_filho-barra-lighthouse-9.jpg&h=a6ee697e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2013/04/Alves_filho-barra-lighthouse-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetapixel.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F04%2FAlves_filho-barra-lighthouse-4.jpg&h=3deb7caf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83811d605895e837292f05ea148795880f041141","tid":666141,"uid":17851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"期待你嘅作品"},{"pid":"cd92e2d3c78d3140e76db8183eae9dd39667a41c","tid":666141,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20c622acf3c34d0b086020c4e801b149145607f3","tid":666141,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd92e2d3c78d3140e76db8183eae9dd39667a41c","tid":666141,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"乜嘢係 巴膠？少上論壇，唔識野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df53975856f74b8fd4c80d261764b30936a76364","tid":666141,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83811d605895e837292f05ea148795880f041141","tid":666141,"uid":17851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"期待你嘅作品"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  努力~~ 希望中意攝影嘅朋友都揾到 啱嘅題材，持續影，影得開心啲~~<br />\n<br />\n冇諗到，幾日前嘅 post，都被你推番上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79b6c63ebd36d918b9f6d76911d594f8fca9c28","tid":666141,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c45eb344fb210fe7f7d3459ac9158601afaaacd","tid":666141,"uid":185452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f79b6c63ebd36d918b9f6d76911d594f8fca9c28","tid":666141,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c622acf3c34d0b086020c4e801b149145607f3","tid":666141,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd92e2d3c78d3140e76db8183eae9dd39667a41c","tid":666141,"uid":55,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"乜嘢係 巴膠？少上論壇，唔識野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:24:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T10:50:22.000Z","msg":"哦哦，原來是咁。<br />\n<br />\n題材 鹹魚青菜，各有所愛啦。<br />\n<br />\n俾我嘅話，若果是 純記錄形式去影巴士，eg 逐個型號、前後左右嘅細節，咁就比較悶。<br />\n<br />\n若果是以藝術形式，就可以多啲發揮。例如 晴天、陰天、雨天下 嘅變化，eg 濺起水花，又或用 pan 嘅形勢，用航拍俯視。都可以有好多玩法。<br />\n<br />\n以下是網上嘅例子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/784/27254173218_80f054e951_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F784%2F27254173218_80f054e951_b.jpg&h=4ebb1a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/969/41002363775_c901b645cc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm1.staticflickr.com%2F969%2F41002363775_c901b645cc_b.jpg&h=898d230c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2882/33535074390_9c710c671c_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm3.staticflickr.com%2F2882%2F33535074390_9c710c671c_b.jpg&h=4dcc3077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4409/36905251552_b990edf008_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm5.staticflickr.com%2F4409%2F36905251552_b990edf008_b.jpg&h=cdc6ff46&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}